&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PhD with 5+ years of experience in academic or industry setting, MS with 10+ years of experience or BS with 12+ years of experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Broad knowledge of genome editing technologies and associated off-target discovery assays (i.e. WGS; targeted sequencing; GUIDE-seq, Digenome-seq discovery / verification; large and small structural variations and translation effects; NGS QC)&lt;/li&gt;
